,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"我成日話自己冇知心朋友<br />\n其實自己潛意識都唔想成為知心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3620648575e0ef335ab58837bd162645fed10119","tid":894661,"uid":7103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"你唔同人親近，人哋試多兩次就唔會再同你親近<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659655016f9626e57f1ef65ccaff8090ee405c7c","tid":894661,"uid":204728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a25e366d8810ea77cbcbbb7220cf26d42af6bfb","tid":894661,"uid":219210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"我係完全唔想人親近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a708b26240ba891c405908f06156b5d13b780d0a","tid":894661,"uid":186163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef658bfb4521f0d971071684e0fd8b873433adf","tid":894661,"uid":49232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得呢個世界唔會有人同自己交心<br />\n之前自己付岀太多 只係換來一句屌你老母<br />\nFd失戀或者俾仔鬧嗰陣 就會拎你嚟岀氣<br />\n<br />\n有時離譜到問兩句 都俾佢地屌話唔放佢地啲嘢上心<br />\n所以同班fd吹水唔會再講自己內心世界<br />\n食飯咪坐係到唔岀聲陪笑囉<br />\n<br />\n返工一個個小圈子 我從來唔會當係啲咩<br />\n只會當你係工具人<br />\n唔理 少理 係最好<br />\n<br />\n屋企就算撚數啦 唔屌你已經偷笑 講完屌返你無撚用<br />\n唔捱得 唔識忍<br />\n<br />\n所以收埋自己係最好"}]}